<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section" id="how">
<div class="container">
  <p class="kicker reveal">How Sustainable Talent works</p>
  <h2 class="reveal">Turn us into your contractor and recruiting engine in three steps</h2>
  <p class="lead reveal">
    We plug into your existing reality, then build and run a model that delivers technical and professional consultants in the United States and across the world without adding internal complexity.
  </p>

  <div class="three-steps">
    <div class="step reveal">
      <div class="tag">
        <div class="n">01</div>
        <div class="t">Design</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Design the right model for your team</h3>
        <p>We align on goals, locations, timelines, budget, and your current vendor mix. Together we define where Sustainable Talent adds the most value as your VSP and global contractor partner.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="side">
        <div style="font-weight:700; color: var(--text-primary);">Output</div>
        <div>Engagement model + governance</div>
        <div>Roles + priority roadmap</div>
        <a class="btn primary" href="#get-started">Book a call</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step reveal">
      <div class="tag">
        <div class="n">02</div>
        <div class="t">Activate</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Stand up TalentOS™ and activate pipelines</h3>
        <p>We configure TalentOS™ for your engagement, connect ADP TotalSource and Deel, and align workflows with your TA and people teams. Then recruiters and sourcers activate pipelines for the roles that matter most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="side">
        <div style="font-weight:700; color: var(--text-primary);">What you see</div>
        <div>Open roles + stages</div>
        <div>Approvals + feedback loops</div>
        <a class="btn primary" href="#platform">Check TalentOS™</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step reveal">
      <div class="tag">
        <div class="n">03</div>
        <div class="t">Refine</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Run the engine and refine as you grow</h3>
        <p>We handle sourcing, screening, offers, onboarding, background checks, compliance, time tracking, payroll, and consultant support. You get clear reporting, a transparent platform, and a partner who tunes the engine as needs evolve.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="side">
        <div style="font-weight:700; color: var(--text-primary);">Coverage</div>
        <div>Full lifecycle delivery</div>
        <div>Program health + reporting</div>
        <a class="btn primary" href="#platform">Explore the platform</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

